=Si Jin=

10
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:39,180
=Episode 7=

11
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,040
- Chief.
- Qi.

12
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,810
Chief, Chuchu is here.

13
00:01:46,810 --> 00:01:47,880
Chuchu is here, Chief.

14
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,120
Qi.

15
00:01:50,790 --> 00:01:51,650
Chief, Chief.

16
00:01:51,650 --> 00:01:52,840
Hurry, Chuchu is here!

17
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,680
Qi.

18
00:01:56,010 --> 00:01:56,850
Qi.

19
00:01:57,970 --> 00:01:59,440
Chief, are you here?

20
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,760
Qi.

21
00:02:00,770 --> 00:02:01,840
Are you here, Chief?

22
00:02:02,370 --> 00:02:03,210
Stop!

23
00:02:08,770 --> 00:02:09,890
Chuchu.

24
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,800
Long time no see.

25
00:02:12,050 --> 00:02:13,800
Surprised? Unexpected?

26
00:02:16,810 --> 00:02:17,890
So surprised.

27
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,050
What brings you to Ling'an?

28
00:02:22,650 --> 00:02:24,000
I've been traveling around,

29
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,010
upholding justice,

30
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:26,810
and before I knew it,
I ended up in Ling'an.

31
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,050
Maybe it's fate,

32
00:02:29,050 --> 00:02:30,210
sensing that you needed me.

33
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:32,210
As expected, as soon as I saw Long Dan,

34
00:02:32,210 --> 00:02:33,490
I heard you were badly injured.

35
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,330
Let me see. Where are you hurt?

36
00:02:37,970 --> 00:02:38,810
Let go.

37
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:41,490
Chuchu,

38
00:02:42,330 --> 00:02:43,370
it's been so many years.

39
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:46,090
Can't you think of yourself
as a young lady?

40
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,380
What should a young lady do?

41
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,720
A young lady should follow rules,

42
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,960
stay away from men,

43
00:02:59,210 --> 00:03:00,520
and get married when she's of age.

44
00:03:05,490 --> 00:03:06,490
I got it.

45
00:03:07,210 --> 00:03:09,210
You must've been pressured
into marriage,

46
00:03:09,650 --> 00:03:10,520
so you ran away.

47
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,810
I have feet.

48
00:03:12,810 --> 00:03:13,720
I can leave anytime.

49
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:16,810
This is walking freely in the world.

50
00:03:16,810 --> 00:03:17,650
Good for you.

51
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,280
Miss Jiang.

52
00:03:26,330 --> 00:03:27,330
Chuchu.

53
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,120
Why are you here?

54
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,930
I live next door,

55
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:34,400
so I came by to check on Commandant Yu.

56
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,650
You mean Qi?

57
00:03:36,930 --> 00:03:38,210
He's inside. Come with me.

58
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,400
Are you friends?

59
00:03:40,770 --> 00:03:41,860
Not only that.

60
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,270
My father is also in the military.

61
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,610
We grew up together.

62
00:03:44,970 --> 00:03:46,120
Even our martial arts master

63
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,000
was the same.

64
00:03:47,530 --> 00:03:48,450
But later,

65
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,450
Qi formed the Chiyu Cavalry

66
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,610
and went to a new camp.

67
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:52,940
That's when we parted ways.

68
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,490
(No wonder I've never seen her.)

69
00:03:55,770 --> 00:03:57,050
(She's really straightforward.)

70
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:58,160
(Yu Qi's been hiding)

71
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,650
(the Chiyu Cavalry,)

72
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:00,930
(but it took her no time)

73
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:02,330
(to tell me everything.)

74
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,840
Miss Jiang,

75
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,170
how do you know Qi?

76
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:07,560
Because...

77
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:09,430
Because of official business.

78
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,720
Then I'll take you in.

79
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,800
OK, let's go.

80
00:04:14,650 --> 00:04:15,490
Qi,

81
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,310
Miss Jiang is here to see you.

82
00:04:20,520 --> 00:04:21,360
Commandant Yu.

83
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,450
Miss Jiang, please sit.

84
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,210
I won't get up to greet you.

85
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:27,130
Don't get up.

86
00:04:27,770 --> 00:04:29,480
Based on your condition now,

87
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,570
you need a few more days
to recover from the poison.

88
00:04:31,890 --> 00:04:33,530
But I need to report

89
00:04:33,530 --> 00:04:35,040
to Capital Security asap,

90
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:37,720
or Mr. Zhen will think

91
00:04:38,450 --> 00:04:39,520
I'm faking,

92
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,160
just staying here enjoying

93
00:04:41,530 --> 00:04:43,010
the fine food you brought.

94
00:04:43,210 --> 00:04:44,090
You have to rest

95
00:04:44,090 --> 00:04:45,160
for a couple of more days.

96
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,680
Aman.

97
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,160
I made pigeon soup

98
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,130
for you today.

99
00:04:56,650 --> 00:04:58,330
Miss Jiang, he's fine.

100
00:04:58,330 --> 00:04:59,430
You don't have to feed him.

101
00:05:00,210 --> 00:05:01,130
Qi,

102
00:05:01,130 --> 00:05:02,090
what's wrong with you?

103
00:05:02,090 --> 00:05:03,160
Just now, you were fine.

104
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,330
You wanted me to...

105
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:05,170
No.

106
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,840
Don't take care of me.

107
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,880
I can handle it.

108
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,640
Chuchu,

109
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:13,250
how long will you stay in Ling'an?

110
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,840
I didn't plan to stay long,

111
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,720
but since I ran into Qi and Long Dan,

112
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,530
I thought I'd stay a little longer.

113
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:20,250
Qi, will you find me annoying?

114
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,560
Of course not.

115
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:27,480
That's good.

116
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,890
Then we can hang out more.

117
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:29,850
OK.

118
00:05:30,770 --> 00:05:32,210
Chuchu, go check

119
00:05:32,210 --> 00:05:34,090
if the medicine Long Dan bought for me

120
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,530
- has arrived.
- Medicine?

121
00:05:35,530 --> 00:05:36,370
Give it to me.

122
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:37,970
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

123
00:05:37,970 --> 00:05:38,810
My pleasure.

124
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,480
Here, Mr. Yu.

125
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:47,130
I'll try it myself.

126
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:49,600
Can you handle it?

127
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:51,050
I can.

128
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:58,170
Let me.

129
00:06:00,450 --> 00:06:01,570
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

130
00:06:20,010 --> 00:06:21,770
You got hurt because of me.

131
00:06:21,890 --> 00:06:22,800
It's only right

132
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,010
that I take care of you.

133
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,650
It's also a way for me

134
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:27,040
to make up for it.

135
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,560
By the way, Mr. Yu,

136
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,890
what would you like to eat tomorrow?

137
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:35,170
Tasty.

138
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,160
Anything tasty will do.

139
00:06:45,820 --> 00:06:50,700
(Grand Princess's Mansion)

140
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:10,860
(Rongyang, Dazhou's Grand Princess)

141
00:07:12,770 --> 00:07:13,620
Mother.

142
00:07:13,620 --> 00:07:15,900
(Cui Mingyue, Rongyang's daughter)
Come in.

143
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,900
(Graceful and Dignified)
The Marquis is coming?

144
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,880
Mingyue,

145
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,600
have you heard

146
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,040
about Marquis Changxing's Mansion?

147
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,920
Of course.

148
00:07:24,330 --> 00:07:25,400
They dug up

149
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,920
over a dozen corpses

150
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,250
in the mansion at once.

151
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,360
Such shocking news

152
00:07:30,650 --> 00:07:31,770
spread throughout Ling'an

153
00:07:31,770 --> 00:07:33,040
in no time.

154
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,200
Your Grace.

155
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:40,120
Mother.

156
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:43,130
How shameless Marquis Changxing is.

157
00:07:43,530 --> 00:07:44,890
His son is so disgraceful,

158
00:07:45,010 --> 00:07:46,890
yet he wanted me to be
his daughter-in-law.

159
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,880
Mingyue,

160
00:07:49,890 --> 00:07:51,690
how many times have I told you

161
00:07:52,570 --> 00:07:54,650
to be more respectful
to Marquis Changxing?

162
00:07:55,330 --> 00:07:56,250
When Nanwu

163
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,210
invaded us,

164
00:07:58,690 --> 00:08:00,090
he and your father

165
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,600
defended the country together.

166
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:04,210
He served the country

167
00:08:06,210 --> 00:08:08,810
and once helped us.

168
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,090
So, Mother,

169
00:08:11,090 --> 00:08:13,010
how are you going to save Cao Xingyu?

170
00:08:14,530 --> 00:08:15,690
Do you have a good plan?

171
00:08:22,570 --> 00:08:24,210
If you personally intervene

172
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:25,400
as the Grand Princess,

173
00:08:25,890 --> 00:08:27,690
the Capital Security
will surely let him go.

174
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,400
The dead are

175
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:31,090
just lowly women.

176
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:32,570
If we give their families

177
00:08:32,570 --> 00:08:34,170
some generous compensation,

178
00:08:34,330 --> 00:08:35,600
everything will be

179
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,050
deescalated, right?

180
00:08:37,290 --> 00:08:38,880
How did you come up with this?

181
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,530
I'm so clever!

182
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,810
You are too naive.

183
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,840
In the future,

184
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,840
I'll have your uncle help you find

185
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:51,170
the best man in the world.

186
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,330
But first,

187
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:53,480
I have to test him.

188
00:08:54,050 --> 00:08:55,240
Only then

189
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:57,530
can I feel at ease.

190
00:08:58,970 --> 00:08:59,940
Mother, you're the best.

191
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,650
The Marquis seeks an audience.

192
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,130
Marquis Changxing.

193
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:14,720
Your Highness,

194
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,640
this is Golden Branch and Jade Leaf.

195
00:09:18,050 --> 00:09:19,930
The branches are made of gold,

196
00:09:20,210 --> 00:09:22,090
the flowers are made
of mutton-fat white jade,

197
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:24,880
and the leaves are made
of high-quality emerald.

198
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:27,090
I managed to get it with great effort

199
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:28,480
from Lingnan.

200
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,290
It's for Your Highness.

201
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,720
You came late at night

202
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,210
because of your son, right?

203
00:09:35,970 --> 00:09:37,840
How insightful you are.

204
00:09:38,050 --> 00:09:39,450
Zhen Heng from the Capital Security,

205
00:09:39,450 --> 00:09:41,290
and Yu Qi, the new Commandant,

206
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:43,410
are bold and reckless,

207
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:45,480
disrespecting me completely.

208
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,690
They fabricated

209
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:48,210
some nonsensical reason

210
00:09:48,210 --> 00:09:49,800
to imprison my son.

211
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,410
They even want to sentence him to death.

212
00:09:51,410 --> 00:09:52,050
Your Highness,

213
00:09:52,690 --> 00:09:54,520
you must stand for me.

214
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,520
Is this charge something you made up,

215
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,480
or is it true?

216
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,440
Your Highness,

217
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,690
everything I said is true.

218
00:10:00,810 --> 00:10:02,530
I wouldn't dare fabricate it.

219
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:05,090
Your Highness, you know

220
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:09,690
he's my only son.

221
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,240
You ask me for help,

222
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,840
yet you won't tell the truth.

223
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,760
How am I supposed to help you?

224
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:19,600
I...

225
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:28,300
(Court, Capital Security)

226
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:19,480
Chief, how's your hand?

227
00:11:20,570 --> 00:11:21,410
It's fine.

228
00:11:21,570 --> 00:11:22,450
Take a look at this.

229
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:24,810
When we searched
Marquis Changxing's Mansion,

230
00:11:24,810 --> 00:11:25,880
we found whips

231
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:26,720
and this

232
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,090
in the secret chamber.

233
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:30,760
I've asked Miss Chi about it.

234
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,450
Cao Xingyu calls this drug

235
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:34,360
Surreal Wander.

236
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,690
Before abusing them every time,

237
00:11:36,690 --> 00:11:38,640
he would take one of them.

238
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,640
- This drug...
- Open it.

239
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:45,360
This drug

240
00:11:45,570 --> 00:11:46,760
is effective.

241
00:11:55,570 --> 00:11:57,120
How could he even take this?

242
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,090
Go ask the physician.

243
00:11:58,090 --> 00:11:59,690
Does he have some chronic illness?

244
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:01,450
I've already asked.

245
00:12:01,450 --> 00:12:02,290
He...

246
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:07,410
This drug...

247
00:12:07,410 --> 00:12:08,930
Come on, spit it out.

248
00:12:10,690 --> 00:12:11,640
It's an aphrodisiac.

249
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:16,690
One of the ingredients

250
00:12:16,690 --> 00:12:18,240
is a plant called bianteng.

251
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:20,530
It only grows in Nanwu.

252
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,050
The physician said

253
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,840
he had only seen this

254
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,640
when Dazhou and Nanwu

255
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:26,640
were still trading,

256
00:12:26,810 --> 00:12:28,570
but now it's banned.

257
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,240
Looks like Cao Xingyu

258
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:39,960
is guilty of more than just murder.

259
00:12:40,770 --> 00:12:42,460
I was just worrying
about having no leads,

260
00:12:42,690 --> 00:12:44,030
and now it's been delivered to me.

261
00:12:44,810 --> 00:12:45,810
Report!

262
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,560
Mr. Yu.

263
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,570
Mr. Zhen.

264
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:50,090
Outside...

265
00:12:50,090 --> 00:12:51,330
Go take a look.

266
00:12:53,330 --> 00:12:55,520
What do Speed Guards do?

267
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,290
They're directly
under the Emperor's command

268
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,700
to investigate the people
and monitor the officials,

269
00:13:00,090 --> 00:13:01,840
with more power than us.

270
00:13:03,210 --> 00:13:04,330
The person who came today

271
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,360
is Commander Han Ran.

272
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,360
Impressive.

273
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:11,880
Mr. Han.

274
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,680
Mr. Han.

275
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:19,020
(Han Ran, Speed Guards Commander)

276
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,090
Marquis,

277
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:23,210
Grand Princess asked me to tell you

278
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:26,120
that she's aware of the situation
with the Capital Security.

279
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:27,720
Please rest assured.

280
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:29,570
Grand Princess said

281
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,810
you were a loyal general of the country,

282
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:34,290
and helping you was helping Dazhou.

283
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,800
(Luxurious and Gorgeous)
Her Highness

284
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,010
also said your son

285
00:13:37,090 --> 00:13:39,210
would have to leave Ling'an

286
00:13:39,810 --> 00:13:41,170
after this.

287
00:13:46,090 --> 00:13:47,880
Please tell Her Highness

288
00:13:48,170 --> 00:13:50,480
I'll send my rebellious son far away.

289
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:52,760
He'll never come back.

290
00:13:53,210 --> 00:13:54,690
(Court)
I came today

