00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:12,410
to eliminate future trouble?

585
00:26:12,410 --> 00:26:13,250
No need.

586
00:26:13,410 --> 00:26:14,770
Cao Xingyu is already useless.

587
00:26:15,130 --> 00:26:16,490
No need to waste another move.

588
00:26:16,970 --> 00:26:17,810
Remember.

589
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:20,120
The more you do,
the more mistakes you make.

590
00:26:20,520 --> 00:26:21,360
Yes.

591
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:22,690
Leave.

592
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:29,780
What will the Capital Security do

593
00:26:30,650 --> 00:26:32,120
about Cao Xingyu's case?

594
00:26:33,450 --> 00:26:34,290
Will they let him go

595
00:26:35,650 --> 00:26:36,730
or execute him?

596
00:26:41,450 --> 00:26:42,970
There's a good show coming up.

597
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:44,930
What do you think?

598
00:26:44,930 --> 00:26:46,240
Does this case have any connection

599
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:47,920
to the Nightingale Division?

600
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:50,530
They're in the dark,
while we're in the light.

601
00:26:50,850 --> 00:26:52,120
They must be waiting

602
00:26:52,410 --> 00:26:53,370
to see how we will

603
00:26:53,370 --> 00:26:54,680
end this show.

604
00:26:56,080 --> 00:26:58,200
Cao Xingyu's guilt is indisputable.

605
00:26:58,650 --> 00:26:59,530
If we release him,

606
00:26:59,890 --> 00:27:01,610
the souls of the murdered women

607
00:27:01,610 --> 00:27:03,290
will never have justice.

608
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:04,530
The Capital Security

609
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:06,730
will lose all credibility.

610
00:27:06,980 --> 00:27:08,040
(Court)
If we execute him,

611
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,970
Marquis Changxing
will lose his only son

612
00:27:10,930 --> 00:27:13,480
so he'll harbor resentment
towards the court

613
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,590
and develop ill intentions.

614
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:16,290
So, no matter what we choose,

615
00:27:16,930 --> 00:27:17,970
it will benefit them

616
00:27:18,370 --> 00:27:20,360
without backfiring.

617
00:27:20,650 --> 00:27:22,200
What a poisonous strategy.

618
00:27:22,930 --> 00:27:23,840
Now,

619
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,730
we truly are in a dilemma.

620
00:27:29,650 --> 00:27:32,120
So, Mr. Zhen, what will you do?

621
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:37,360
Mozi once said

622
00:27:37,850 --> 00:27:39,160
that the law is necessary

623
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,530
to rule the country.

624
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,460
Only when all people,
noble or humble, follow the law

625
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,440
can peace be achieved.

626
00:27:46,370 --> 00:27:47,210
So,

627
00:27:48,890 --> 00:27:51,250
following your heart
and adhering to the law

628
00:27:51,850 --> 00:27:53,840
is the correct solution to this problem.

629
00:28:02,890 --> 00:28:03,840
Miss Jiang,

630
00:28:04,130 --> 00:28:05,600
the wrongdoer should be punished.

631
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:07,040
Should we just stand by

632
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:08,600
and watch that villain go free?

633
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,280
Should my daughter

634
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:13,250
die without justice?

635
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:16,440
Ms. Xiu, please calm down.

636
00:28:17,610 --> 00:28:19,130
I have thought of a method,

637
00:28:19,130 --> 00:28:20,200
but it's a bit risky.

638
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:21,610
I'm not sure

639
00:28:21,610 --> 00:28:22,920
if you're willing to try.

640
00:28:23,610 --> 00:28:24,450
Commandant Yu,

641
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:26,920
among the generals in Ling'an,

642
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:29,250
few are as wise, courteous,

643
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:30,880
and eloquent as you.

644
00:28:31,210 --> 00:28:32,680
You must've read many books.

645
00:28:33,170 --> 00:28:35,090
May I ask who your master was?

646
00:28:35,490 --> 00:28:37,130
Why did you choose to study martial arts

647
00:28:37,210 --> 00:28:38,360
instead of literature?

648
00:28:39,610 --> 00:28:41,330
That's a long story.

649
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:43,970
For now, we should focus

650
00:28:43,970 --> 00:28:45,770
on how to handle this case.

651
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,920
Even if we rule impartially,

652
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:49,670
we have to end it in three days.

653
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,450
If they come to take him then,

654
00:28:51,450 --> 00:28:52,640
we'll have to hand him over.

655
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:56,400
When they get Cao Xingyu,

656
00:28:56,930 --> 00:28:59,120
the testimony might change,

657
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:02,570
and they might find a Nanwu scapegoat.

658
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:04,970
Then the trial

659
00:29:05,610 --> 00:29:06,770
would be meaningless.

660
00:29:06,970 --> 00:29:07,970
You're right.

661
00:29:10,080 --> 00:29:11,680
What should we do?

662
00:29:12,890 --> 00:29:15,160
We should have His Majesty
preside over the trial.

663
00:29:15,180 --> 00:29:17,320
We should ask His Majesty
to preside over the trial.

664
00:29:26,510 --> 00:29:27,700
Candied hawthorn.

665
00:29:29,220 --> 00:29:30,410
Sir, have a look.

666
00:29:30,410 --> 00:29:31,570
We're in a bustling market.

667
00:29:31,890 --> 00:29:33,080
You must not be seen.

668
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:34,900
(Eunuch Liu from the Palace)
What if someone

669
00:29:34,930 --> 00:29:35,770
recognizes you?

670
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:40,920
Wait.

671
00:29:41,650 --> 00:29:42,490
Stop.

672
00:29:43,610 --> 00:29:44,450
Your Majesty.

673
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:46,880
Master.

674
00:29:47,450 --> 00:29:48,880
Go buy a cold drink.

675
00:29:49,560 --> 00:29:50,620
We're traveling incognito,

676
00:29:50,620 --> 00:29:52,370
so we didn't bring many guards with us.

677
00:29:52,370 --> 00:29:54,520
Only the Capital Security
is patrolling secretly.

678
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,650
It's unnecessary to me.

679
00:29:55,650 --> 00:29:57,050
Stop talking and go buy it.

680
00:29:57,690 --> 00:29:58,530
Yes.

681
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,320
Get me one.

682
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,360
Sure.

683
00:30:08,080 --> 00:30:08,920
Take care.

684
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:17,560
Master.

685
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,080
Let's go.

686
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,600
Your Majesty,

687
00:30:40,930 --> 00:30:41,880
I've been wronged.

688
00:30:42,170 --> 00:30:44,120
Please seek justice for me.

689
00:30:47,650 --> 00:30:48,490
Take her away.

690
00:30:50,320 --> 00:30:51,240
Your Majesty!

691
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,090
Wait.

692
00:31:10,080 --> 00:31:10,970
Ma'am.

693
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:13,100
(Emperor Jingming of Dazhou)
Continue.

694
00:31:13,130 --> 00:31:13,970
Your Majesty,

695
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:16,120
I had no other choice

696
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:18,360
but to risk my life and appeal to you.

697
00:31:18,690 --> 00:31:20,600
Please seek justice for me.

698
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,000
Please give justice

699
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,160
to my deceased daughter.

700
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,920
Why not report it?

701
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:27,390
The Capital Security wouldn't help?

702
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:32,120
The murderer holds a high position

703
00:31:32,760 --> 00:31:33,970
and can cover up everything.

704
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:36,650
My daughter isn't the only victim.

705
00:31:36,650 --> 00:31:39,330
He killed over a dozen young girls
of similar age.

706
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:40,560
The Capital Security

707
00:31:40,560 --> 00:31:41,770
only just arrested him,

708
00:31:42,210 --> 00:31:43,600
but before the case is closed,

709
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:45,160
someone is already intervening.

710
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:48,250
It's likely he'll be released

711
00:31:49,130 --> 00:31:50,680
in a few days.

712
00:31:52,170 --> 00:31:53,810
Who is so audacious?

713
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:56,290
Cao Xingyu,

714
00:31:56,650 --> 00:31:57,880
Marquis Changxing's heir.

715
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:03,930
(Graceful and Dignified)
I never expected

716
00:32:03,930 --> 00:32:05,490
something to go wrong with my son.

717
00:32:05,610 --> 00:32:06,600
Sorry for the trouble.

718
00:32:06,930 --> 00:32:09,040
Your Highness, you are influential.

719
00:32:09,040 --> 00:32:09,970
Your words matter.

720
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:12,080
I hope you can help me once more.

721
00:32:12,370 --> 00:32:13,880
If I can overcome this obstacle,

722
00:32:15,890 --> 00:32:18,370
I will follow your lead

723
00:32:18,370 --> 00:32:19,760
without hesitation.

724
00:32:19,760 --> 00:32:21,250
You've become too greedy.

725
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,600
I was deceived by you before,

726
00:32:25,080 --> 00:32:26,480
so I tried to help out of goodwill.

727
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,160
That's the limit of my kindness.

728
00:32:28,450 --> 00:32:30,970
Yet your son committed a heinous crime.

729
00:32:31,410 --> 00:32:33,440
Perhaps this is his fate.

730
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:35,320
Marquis,

731
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:39,970
it's time to accept your fate.

732
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,080
Fate?

733
00:32:49,850 --> 00:32:51,290
Is this my fate?

734
00:32:55,370 --> 00:32:56,800
I beg your pardon for my rudeness.

735
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:57,800
Now, don't you think

736
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:59,970
it's too late for you

737
00:32:59,970 --> 00:33:01,480
to distance yourself from me?

738
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:03,850
If you accidentally caused harm,

739
00:33:03,850 --> 00:33:05,680
then that too is your fate,
Your Highness.

740
00:33:05,930 --> 00:33:07,640
Since you're ungrateful,

741
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:09,640
fine.

742
00:33:09,930 --> 00:33:11,200
Present it to the Marquis.

743
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:15,240
Your son

744
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,920
traded the intelligence of Dazhou

745
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,850
for Surreal Wander

746
00:33:18,850 --> 00:33:20,690
with Nanwu's Nightingale Division

747
00:33:20,690 --> 00:33:22,200
to satisfy his lust.

748
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:24,720
Impossible.

749
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:25,970
This is impossible!

750
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:27,170
My son, however outrageous,

751
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:28,720
would never do such a thing.

752
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:29,880
This must be slander!

753
00:33:30,890 --> 00:33:31,840
It's fine.

754
00:33:32,690 --> 00:33:34,160
Speed Guards

755
00:33:35,210 --> 00:33:37,050
have many letters like this.

756
00:33:38,410 --> 00:33:39,770
Whether it's a misunderstanding

757
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,200
is clear in the letters.

758
00:33:43,650 --> 00:33:45,850
Your Highness, I deserve to die.

759
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:47,200
Please forgive me.

760
00:33:47,610 --> 00:33:49,010
Please tell me

761
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,730
what I should do.

762
00:33:52,850 --> 00:33:54,440
This is a farce.

763
00:33:55,130 --> 00:33:56,440
It's time for it to end.

764
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:58,250
Although my son is rebellious,

765
00:33:59,410 --> 00:34:00,970
he's still my only son.

766
00:34:00,970 --> 00:34:01,810
Your Highness!

767
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,880
If it were just a dozen young women,

768
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:07,730
the most it'd cost
is the life of the heir.

769
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,970
But this is treason.

770
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:13,160
Your entire family

771
00:34:13,330 --> 00:34:14,800
cannot be spared.

772
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,570
What's more important?

773
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,370
Do I need to say more?

774
00:34:32,370 --> 00:34:33,490
Since you

775
00:34:33,930 --> 00:34:35,290
brought this treasure

776
00:34:35,290 --> 00:34:36,890
(Graceful and Dignified)
from Lingnan,

777
00:34:37,200 --> 00:34:39,800
I cannot take this from you.

778
00:34:40,080 --> 00:34:41,280
I've admired it enough.

779
00:34:41,810 --> 00:34:43,600
It's time for you to take it back.

780
00:34:49,520 --> 00:34:52,680
Golden Branch and Jade Leaf.

781
00:34:53,680 --> 00:34:56,890
Just as the name suggests.

782
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:14,740
(Tiande Hall, Palace)

783
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:17,520
Your Majesty.

784
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,800
With both witness and physical evidence,

785
00:35:28,970 --> 00:35:30,530
what can you argue?

786
00:35:30,810 --> 00:35:31,650
Father.

787
00:35:32,770 --> 00:35:33,610
Father.

788
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,000
Your Majesty, I...

789
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,840
Your Majesty.

790
00:35:37,770 --> 00:35:38,600
I'm guilty.

791
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,470
Do not speak recklessly.

792
00:35:40,470 --> 00:35:41,110
Cao Yong.

793
00:35:42,610 --> 00:35:44,860
A father should be responsible
for his ill-bred child.

794
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:46,680
Since my son was young,

795
00:35:46,970 --> 00:35:49,200
whenever his father
was unsatisfied with him,

796
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:51,320
he'd receive a cruel beating.

797
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,850
I was weak and useless,

798
00:35:54,410 --> 00:35:55,930
so I failed to stop him.

799
00:35:57,330 --> 00:35:58,760
As his parents, we bear great sin

800
00:35:58,930 --> 00:36:01,730
for what he's done.

801
00:36:01,730 --> 00:36:03,080
Enough! Shut up!

802
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:04,570
Don't you dare hit my mother!

803
00:36:08,930 --> 00:36:09,770
Your Majesty,

804
00:36:10,680 --> 00:36:13,090
we failed to teach our child,

805
00:36:13,330 --> 00:36:15,120
so he has gone astray.

806
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:16,680
Your Majesty,

807
00:36:17,450 --> 00:36:18,970
please

808
00:36:19,330 --> 00:36:20,680
spare his life.

809
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:22,320
Mother.

810
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:23,360
Mother.

811
00:36:23,370 --> 00:36:24,210
Mother.

812
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:26,000
Mother.

813
00:36:28,810 --> 00:36:31,760
If I show mercy to the heir,

814
00:36:32,250 --> 00:36:33,570
what will happen to the law?

815
00:36:47,850 --> 00:36:49,200
A life for a life.

816
00:36:52,370 --> 00:36:53,720
Before I came here,

817
00:36:54,930 --> 00:36:55,890
I poisoned myself.

818
00:36:57,200 --> 00:36:59,240
I hope my life

819
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:02,050
can soothe the souls.

820
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:03,400
Mother.

821
00:37:03,850 --> 00:37:04,690
Mother.

822
00:37:05,040 --> 00:37:05,880
Mother!

823
00:37:05,970 --> 00:37:07,330
Mother, I'm sorry.

824
00:37:07,330 --> 00:37:09,280
Mother, Mother!

825
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,490
Mother!

826
00:37:34,200 --> 00:37:35,640
Spread His Majesty's decree:

827
00:37:36,200 --> 00:37:38,250
Cao Xingyu, Marquis Changxing's heir,

828
00:37:38,250 --> 00:37:40,890
kidnapped common women, abused his wife,

829
00:37:40,890 --> 00:37:43,280
and trampled on human life.
His crimes are unforgivable.

830
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:45,200
He will be executed after the autumn.

831
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:48,480
Cao Yong, Marquis Changxing,
failed to educate his son.

832
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,090
Considering his military achievements,

833
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:51,450
his title will be retained

834
00:37:51,450 --> 00:37:53,530
but will not be inherited.

835
00:37:53,890 --> 00:37:56,640
The decree becomes effective
upon arrival.

836
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:04,260
(Tiande Hall)

837
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:06,290
How considerate of you.

838
00:38:06,290 --> 00:38:07,200
I'm sorry.

839
00:38:07,410 --> 00:38:08,250
How did she manage

840
00:38:08,250 --> 00:38:09,490
to tell me this?

841
00:38:09,770 --> 00:38:11,100
How did she recognize me

842
00:38:11,100 --> 00:38:12,160
among all those palanquins

843
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,120
in the street?

844
00:38:13,640 --> 00:38:14,480
I shouldn't have

845
00:38:15,160 --> 00:38:17,050
used my position in the Capital Security

846
00:38:17,290 --> 00:38:18,160
to force Your Majesty

847
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:19,770
to interrogate Marquis Changxing's heir.

848
00:38:19,890 --> 00:38:21,320
This trial today

849
00:38:22,080 --> 00:38:24,120
has cost Marquis Changxing his heir

850
00:38:24,290 --> 00:38:25,290
and his wife.

851
00:38:25,290 --> 00:38:27,200
Do you know who Marquis Changxing is?

852
00:38:27,410 --> 00:38:28,320
I do.

853
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,400
In terms of loyalty,

854
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:32,050
you two have risked your lives

855
00:38:32,850 --> 00:38:33,690
to serve the country.

856
00:38:34,080 --> 00:38:35,160
In the court,

857
00:38:35,730 --> 00:38:37,170
he's one of your trusted officials.

858
00:38:37,250 --> 00:38:38,570
Today, Your Majesty's actions

859
00:38:38,890 --> 00:38:40,280
have chilled his heart.

860
00:38:41,290 --> 00:38:42,450
In the future,

861
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:44,160
he may never again serve the country.

862
00:38:44,810 --> 00:38:45,730
But, Your Majesty,

863
00:38:45,730 --> 00:38:47,090
I had no other choice.

864
00:38:47,850 --> 00:38:49,970
What's more important, a dozen lives

865
00:38:49,970 --> 00:38:51,290
or the Marquis's son

866
00:38:51,290 --> 00:38:53,010
who should've been punished?

867
00:38:53,450 --> 00:38:54,680
I'm too short-sighted

868
00:38:55,450 --> 00:38:56,890
to think of something better.

869
00:38:56,890 --> 00:38:58,050
Are you saying

870
00:38:58,370 --> 00:38:59,970
I can't tell right from wrong

